Job Level
Non-Management
Assists the Outlet/Restaurant Manager/Head Waiter with the day-to-day operation of the outlet in accordance with established policies and procedures, acting on their behalf in their absence.
Interacts with guests in each of the outlets to solicit comments.
Communicates with the Outlet/Restaurant Manager/Head Waiter any difficulties, guest comments and other relevant information.
To demonstrate the 12-Service Excellence Basics and ensure that all Outlet/Restaurant colleagues continually follows the same.
Prepares daily assignments of personnel based on the volume of business.
Prepares and implements the outlets promotions / theme nights.
To monitor and ensure that the daily revenue is deposited with the front office cashier and summarized properly according to the guidelines set by the Accounts Department.
To ensure that the P.O.S machine is in full implementation.
Keeps updated with new products in the market.
